<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ḥllt qydy sydy ʿndmạ kạn ạlmḥạl
 bạ̉n ạ̉ḥl mʿṣmy mn qywd kạljbạl
 ạlqrạr - tḥbny fy ʿạlm lạ yʿrf mʿny̱ llḥb
 tḥbny thtm by tmsẖy mʿy fy kl drb
 fạ̉frḥ wạ̉kẖbr bkẖạlq qd ṣạr ậb
 2- rfʿt rạ̉sy sydy ʿndmạ knt ḥzyn
 msḥt dmʿ mqlty mbdlạaⁿ kẖwfy yqyn
 3- qbltny fy bytk wqthạ knt fqyr
 wkẖạtmạaⁿ ậlbstny jạʿlạaⁿ mny ạ̉myr
 4- hl ạ̉stḥq kl dẖạ yạ krymạaⁿ fy ạlʿṭạʾ
 whl lḥbk mdy̱ lạ̹nthạʾ ạlkwn lạ</lyrics>
<title>ḥllt qydy sydy</title>
</song>